.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, kale, peas
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, spy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, pop, r&b
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, scrabble
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, swimming
 1. the person eating kale is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating peas##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person playing whist and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person playing whist is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the person playing whist is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | peas      | kale      | cabbage      |
| Hobby         | fishing   | skydiving | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | satire    | spy          |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | folk      | r&b          |
| Game   | whist    | bridge  | scrabble      |
| Pet           | hamster   | hedgehog  | mouse        |
| Sport         | climbing  | sailing   | swimming     |

